Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:39.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}縱使相互呼喚未曾停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:48.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}卻入歧途 眼見漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.34,0:22:59.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}相互吸引的紅與黑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:06.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}相互追逐的光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:14.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}相對而生的兩極 紛繁演化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:18.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}孕育世間萬物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:25.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}正因有你 方得有我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:30.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}縱兩相隔 亦在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:31.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)\an1}在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:37.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}世間眾生皆非完美無瑕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:44.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}而所欠缺的那重要部分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.18,0:23:51.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}只能不住追尋
